    		<h2>Help ensure hourly workers can get enough hours so their paycheck covers the bills and puts food on the table.</h2>

            <p>San Jose has a <%= link_to 'crisis of underemployment', '/why.html', :target => '_blank' %>. To avoid paying fair wages and benefits, too many employers hire new part-time workers instead of giving hours to current employees.</p>

            <p><%= link_to 'Measure E', '/about.html', :target => '_blank' %> &mdash; on the November ballot &mdash; will require businesses to offer any available additional hours to their current, qualified part-time employees before hiring more workers.</p>

